    "body": "This PR adds the missing select_gemm_impl method with the correct logic to support LoRA in CompressedTensorsWNA16MoEMethod. Without this implementation, attempting to use LoRA results in the following error:\n\n```\nvllm1-1  | (Worker_TP0 pid=43) ERROR 12-27 16:09:54 [multiproc_executor.py:751]   File \"/usr/local/lib/python3.12/dist-packages/vllm/lora/layers/fused_moe.py\", line 57, in __init__\n\nvllm1-1  | (Worker_TP0 pid=43) ERROR 12-27 16:09:54 [multiproc_executor.py:751]     self._inject_lora_into_fused_moe()\n\nvllm1-1  | (Worker_TP0 pid=43) ERROR 12-27 16:09:54 [multiproc_executor.py:751]   File \"/usr/local/lib/python3.12/dist-packages/vllm/lora/layers/fused_moe.py\", line 129, in _inject_lora_into_fused_moe\n\nvllm1-1  | (Worker_TP0 pid=43) ERROR 12-27 16:09:54 [multiproc_executor.py:751]     self.base_layer.quant_method.select_gemm_impl(\n\nvllm1-1  | (Worker_TP0 pid=43) ERROR 12-27 16:09:54 [multiproc_executor.py:751]   File \"/usr/local/lib/python3.12/dist-packages/vllm/model_executor/layers/fused_moe/fused_moe_method_base.py\", line 69, in select_gemm_impl\n\nvllm1-1  | (Worker_TP0 pid=43) ERROR 12-27 16:09:54 [multiproc_executor.py:751]     raise NotImplementedError(\n\nvllm1-1  | (Worker_TP0 pid=43) ERROR 12-27 16:09:54 [multiproc_executor.py:751] NotImplementedError: CompressedTensorsWNA16MoEMethod must select appropriate gemm implementation based on the prepare_finalize\n\nvllm1-1  | (Worker_TP3 pid=46) INFO 12-27 16:09:54 [multiproc_executor.py:709] Parent process exited, terminating worker\n```",
    "created_at": "2025-12-28T13:15:49Z",
